<div class="med-history" id="aboutUs">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row align-items-end">
            <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
                <h2>About Us</h2>

                <p>
                    We offer a private off-campus living environment that supports each student's academic experience at university.
                    We strive towards creating a community that fosters safety/security, personal development/growth and the rendering of professional services. We are further more committed to be responsive to the needs of all residents and to be driven by the ideal of realising a better quality of student life in our residence.
                </p>

                <a class="d-inline-block button gradient-bg" href="#">Read More</a>
            </div>

            <div class="col-12 col-lg-6 mt-5 mt-lg-0">
                <img class="responsive" src="images/about.jpg" alt="">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="faq-stuff" id="help" style="background-image: url(/help/images/faq-bg.jpg); background-attachment:fixed;">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-12">
                <h2>FAQ & HELP</h2>
            </div>

            <div class="col-12 col-lg-6 mb-5 mb-lg-0">
                <div class="accordion-wrap type-accordion">
                    <h3 class="entry-title d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center"> Q. How Can I Make Payment For My Accommodation Fees? <span class="arrow-r"></span></h3>

                    <div class="entry-content">
                        <p> A. Contact our Office for details </p>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="entry-title d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center"> Q. Do You Guys Have Laundry Facilities? <span class="arrow-r"></span></h3>

                    <div class="entry-content">
                        <p> A. Yes, we do. A washing machine, dryer and basin for handwash. </p>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="entry-title d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center"> Q. Can I Have A Guest To Sleepover? <span class="arrow-r"></span></h3>

                    <div class="entry-content">
                        <p> A. Yes, the student will be requested payment R100 per night each person. </p>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="entry-title d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center"> Q. What Is Provided In Each Room? <span class="arrow-r"></span></h3>

                    <div class="entry-content">
                        <p> A. A base, mattress, wardrobe, study desk & desk chair, shelving unit, tall mirror. </p>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="entry-title d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center"> Q. How Do I Report A Fault So It Can Be Repaired? <span class="arrow-r"></span></h3>

                    <div class="entry-content">
                        <p> A. To report a fault, please complete the fault form online. If the fault is an emergency please contact Hope Corner reception on 041 369 5943. </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-12 col-lg-6 mt-5 mt-lg-0">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                        <div class="professional-box">
                            <h2 class="d-flex align-items-center">Staff</h2>

                            <img src="images/cardiogram-2.png" alt="">

                            <p>
                                Student Bookings<br />
                                Admin clicks the student bookings link when he or she wants to check the recent bookings. They can also use this page to accept or deny the booking made by the student.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                        <div class="quality-box">
                            <h2 class="d-flex align-items-center">Student</h2>

                            <img src="images/hospital.png" alt="">

                            <p>
                                MAKE BOOKING<br /><br />
                                Make booking takes you to the booking page, where you can complete the booking form only if you have decided that you want to book your stay with us.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

